Hello <%= @vps.user.login %>,

VPS #<%= @vps.id %> (<%= @vps.hostname %>) is nearing expiration.

<% if @expires_in_a_day -%>
It expires in less than one day.
<% elsif @expires_in_days && @expires_in_days >= 0 -%>
It expires in approximately <%= @expires_in_days.ceil %> days.
<% else -%>
It expired approximately <%= @expired_days_ago.ceil %> days ago.
<% end -%>
<% if @state && @state.expiration_date -%>
Expiration date: <%= local_time(@state.expiration_date, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M %Z') %>
<% end -%>
<% if @base_url && !@base_url.empty? -%>
vpsAdmin: <%= @base_url %>
<% end -%>

Best regards,

vpsAdmin
